flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[User Initiates Payment or P2P Transfer]
    B --> C{Is User Authenticated?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Proceed to Payment Processing]
    C -->|No| E[Prompt User to Authenticate]
    E --> B
    D --> F[Secure Payment Gateway]
    F --> G[Transaction Success?]
    G -->|Yes| H[Update Transaction History]
    G -->|No| I[Handle Payment Failure]
    H --> J[Ensure Compliance Checks]
    J --> K[Notify User of Successful Transaction]
    I --> L[Notify User of Payment Failure]
    K --> M[End]
    L --> M